- Build and run the test suite
- Update the version number in wscript
- Nuke old versions, check that the new version can install cleanly
- Run new benchmarks
- Rebuild the documentation
- Upload new documentation to Sourceforge page
- Check that the wiki page is up to date
- Create a new version in trac
- Upload the tarball to the file release system
- Mark the new release as the latest version
- Tag the release
- Update project info on freecode.com
